directions: Combine chickpeas, 1/2 the reserved liquid, prunes, olive oil, tahini, stevia, and salt in the bowl of a food processor. Process until smooth.
ingredients: 1 (15 ounce) can canned chickpeas (garbanzo beans), drained with liquid reserved
5  pitted prunes, or more to taste
1 tablespoon stevia sugar substitute (such as Truvia®)
title: Sweet Hummus
